29:56.966 --> 29:59.298
OF--OF COURSE. THAT--
THAT MAKES PERFECT SENSE--

29:59.298 --> 30:03.302
UH, YOUR NAME BEING BENFORD,
HER NAME BEING BENFORD.

30:03.302 --> 30:05.304
UH...

30:05.304 --> 30:07.476
(singsong voice)
