30:30.129 --> 30:33.102
HEY, HONEY.

30:33.102 --> 30:35.104
(whoosh)

30:37.266 --> 30:41.010
(chuckles)

30:41.010 --> 30:42.611
YOU'RE HER.

30:42.611 --> 30:44.243
