30:47.046 --> 30:48.277
UM...

30:48.277 --> 30:50.249
YOU KNOW, CHARLIE...

30:50.249 --> 30:52.952
WHY DON'T WE DOUBLE CHECK
YOUR CANDY IN THE KITCHEN?
(Nicole) GOOD IDEA.

30:52.952 --> 30:56.025
