31:04.863 --> 31:07.366
WHY?
THIS IS MY HOUSE, TOO.

31:07.366 --> 31:11.540
(whoosh)
IT'S YOUR HOUSE, TOO, DYLAN.

31:11.540 --> 31:13.042
(whoosh)

31:13.042 --> 31:15.204
HE KEEPS SAYING THAT.

31:15.204 --> 31:18.447
DYLAN IS AUTISTIC.
THE REPETITIVE SPEECH--

31:18.447 --> 31:20.579
I DON'T NEED A DIAGNOSIS.

31:22.651 --> 31:25.985
NOW I UNDERSTAND.

31:25.985 --> 31:27.556
WHAT?

31:27.556 --> 31:30.159
WHY I MADE HER--
WHY I MADE YOU SO--

31:30.159 --> 31:31.390
UNCOMFORTABLE?
YES.

31:31.390 --> 31:33.492
UM, OKAY, CLEARLY, UM,

31:33.492 --> 31:36.565
