FOR EVERYBODY.

31:43.632 --> 31:46.175
YOU LEAVE...

31:46.175 --> 31:49.038
YOU DON'T COME BACK.

31:57.386 --> 32:02.121
I'M VERY SORRY IF WE'VE
CAUSED YOU ANY INCONVENIENCE.

32:02.121 --> 32:04.123
THANK YOU...

32:04.123 --> 32:06.025
BOTH...

32:06.025 --> 32:08.327
FOR THE KINDNESS
YOU'VE SHOWN DYLAN.

32:20.209 --> 32:22.271
THANK YOU.

32:22.271 --> 32:24.213
IT'S MY HOUSE, TOO.

32:24.213 --> 32:27.276
(whispers) OKAY. COME ON.
GOOD NIGHT, OLIVIA.

32:27.276 --> 32:29.278
(Lloyd) COME ON, DYLAN.
LET'S GO.

32:29.278 --> 32:31.280
GOOD NIGHT, DYLAN.

32:31.280 --> 32:33.282
(door closes)

32:35.184 --> 32:36.525
LOOKS LIKE THE PARTY'S OVER.

32:36.525 --> 32:39.358
DEFINITELY OVER.

32:57.246 --> 32:59.248
(Demetri) FBI!

33:31.180 --> 33:34.083
(whoosh)

33:39.388 --> 33:45.023
THESE CAME FROM A FRIEND
OF YOURS NAMED MAYA...

33:45.023 --> 33:47.326
WORRIED ABOUT YOU.

33:49.798 --> 33:52.461
YOU OKAY?

33:57.066 --> 33:59.608
WHEN I GOT SHOT...

34:01.670 --> 34:03.712
THE BULLET...

34:03.712 --> 34:07.176
BOUNCED AROUND
ALL OVER THE PLACE.

34:07.176 --> 34:11.450
THE ONLY THING
THEY SAID THEY COULD DO

34:11.450 --> 34:14.483
WITHOUT TAKING
THE WHOLE THING OUT...

34:17.086 --> 34:20.058
OLIVIA DID THIS THING
CALLED A B-LYNCH.

34:22.060 --> 34:25.564
(voice breaking)
BUT WITH ALL THE SCARRING...

34:25.564 --> 34:27.336
(sniffles)

34:27.336 --> 34:31.570
THEY SAID THAT IT'S GONNA
BE ALMOST IMPOSSIBLE...

34:33.572 --> 34:36.175
(crying)

34:36.175 --> 34:37.846
WHY AM I CRYING?

34:37.846 --> 34:43.782
I NEVER EVEN WANTED
TO HAVE A BABY.

34:43.782 --> 34:46.115
IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.

34:46.115 --> 34:49.858
(crying)

34:56.865 --> 34:58.527
(blows)

35:03.472 --> 35:06.375
I CAN SEE WHY YOU LIKE HIM.
HE'S VERY CHARMING.

35:06.375 --> 35:08.637
I DON'T LIKE HIM. COME ON.

35:08.637 --> 35:11.610
CAN YOU STOP SO WE CAN
ACTUALLY TALK ABOUT THIS?
(dishes clattering loudly)

35:11.610 --> 35:14.143
I DON'T LIKE HIM.

35:14.143 --> 35:16.845
HE'S THE FATHER
OF ONE OF MY PATIENTS.

35:16.845 --> 35:18.847
I KNOW WHO HE IS.

35:18.847 --> 35:22.421
WHAT I WANT TO KNOW IS
HOW HIS SON FOUND HIS WAY HERE.
I HAVE NO IDEA.

35:22.421 --> 35:24.823
REALLY?
YEAH.

35:24.823 --> 35:28.857
WELL, I'M A LITTLE CONFUSED,
BECAUSE I THOUGHT YOU SAID

35:28.857 --> 35:31.830
YOU HAD DYLAN
MOVED OFF YOUR ROTATION.
I DID.

35:31.830 --> 35:33.662
YOU DID?

35:36.305 --> 35:38.637
THEN WHY ARE YOU LISTED
AS THE ATTENDING

35:38.637 --> 35:40.869
ON HIS WRISTBAND?
OH, GOD.

35:40.869 --> 35:43.212
