TO DO WITH THAT.

35:43.212 --> 35:47.145
MY BOSS MADETHE DECISION.
YOUR BOSS ALSO TELL YOU
NOT TO SAY ANYTHING ABOUT IT?

35:47.145 --> 35:49.448
NO, I DIDN'T SAY ANYTHING
ABOUT IT BECAUSE I THOUGHT

35:49.448 --> 35:52.451
IT WOULD MAKE A HORRENDOUS
SITUATION THAT MUCH WORSE.

35:52.451 --> 35:55.153
