INTO SOMEONE I'M NOT.
DON'T YOU TURN THIS AROUND
AND MAKE IT ABOUT ME.

36:01.360 --> 36:03.532
THE MAN YOU MIGHT BE SLEEPING
WITH IN SIX MONTHS' TIME

36:03.532 --> 36:06.395
WAS JUST IN OUR LIVING ROOM,
AND I SURE AS HELL

36:06.395 --> 36:09.198
