INTO OUR LIVES. YOU DID!
THAT'S NOT FAIR.

36:09.198 --> 36:11.400
JUST BE HONEST.
JUST BE HONEST.

36:11.400 --> 36:13.742
HAVE--HAVE YOU BEEN
TALKING TO HIM AT WORK?

36:13.742 --> 36:17.346
OH, COME ON! COME ON, MARK.

36:17.346 --> 36:21.250
HUH? HAVE YOU DONE ANYTHING
ELSE I SHOULD KNOW ABOUT?
MARK, DON'T INTERROGATE ME.

36:21.250 --> 36:24.182
THEN BE HONEST WITH ME!
I AM!

36:24.182 --> 36:26.755
ARE YOU BEING HONEST
WITH ME?

36:26.755 --> 36:28.457
OH, WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

36:28.457 --> 36:31.320
ALL THE OLD PATTERNS
ARE BACK, MARK.

36:31.320 --> 36:34.723
YOU'RE OUT OF THE HOUSE
ALL THE TIME.

36:34.723 --> 36:37.426
