AND MORE SECRETIVE.

36:37.426 --> 36:40.569
SO I'M ASKING YOU THE SAME THING
THAT YOU ASKED ME...

36:40.569 --> 36:42.571
BE HONEST.

36:42.571 --> 36:47.436
ARE YOU HIDING
ANYTHING FROM ME?

36:47.436 --> 36:49.438
(silverware clinking)

36:51.880 --> 36:53.842
MARK?

36:58.917 --> 37:00.989
(lowered voice)
IN MY FLASH-FORWARD...

37:03.252 --> 37:05.724
I WAS DRINKING.

37:07.796 --> 37:09.528
WOW.

37:14.763 --> 37:16.835
HERE WE ARE AGAIN.

37:16.835 --> 37:19.468
OLIVIA,
THIS ISN'T LIKE BEFORE.

37:19.468 --> 37:21.239
