37:21.239 --> 37:23.241
WHAT? NO, IT HASN'T.
THIS ISN'T THE SAME.

37:23.241 --> 37:25.774
DON'T CONDEMN ME FOR
SOMETHING I HAVEN'T DONE YET.

37:25.774 --> 37:28.677
DID YOU EVEN HEAR
WHAT YOU JUST SAID?

37:28.677 --> 37:31.019
YOU'VE BEEN PUNISHING ME
THIS WHOLE TIME

37:31.019 --> 37:33.652
FOR AN IMAGINARY
RELATIONSHIP.

37:33.652 --> 37:37.586
