YOU WANT TO BE LET OFF THE HOOK.

37:37.586 --> 37:40.459
BUT OUR PAST TOGETHER,
MARK--

37:40.459 --> 37:43.692
ALL WE'VE BEEN THROUGH
WITH YOUR DRINKING...

37:43.692 --> 37:46.595
THAT'S REAL.

37:46.595 --> 37:50.038
THAT STILL HURTS.

37:50.038 --> 37:53.872
I'M NOT GOING
THROUGH IT AGAIN.

37:53.872 --> 37:56.605
I PROMISE YOU...

37:56.605 --> 37:57.906
I'M NOT GONNA DRINK.

37:57.906 --> 37:59.978
BUT IT'S NOT
ABOUT THE DRINKING.

37:59.978 --> 38:02.781
YOU KNOW THAT.

38:02.781 --> 38:05.954
IT'S ABOUT TRUST.

38:05.954 --> 38:09.958
IT'S ABOUT TRUST, AND WE DON'T
TRUST EACH OTHER ANYMORE.

38:11.990 --> 38:16.325
SO EVERYTHING WE SAID
AT THE HOSPITAL TODAY

38:16.325 --> 38:20.729
