38:24.873 --> 38:26.735
IT'S NOT A LIE.

38:26.735 --> 38:28.937
IT'S WHAT I WANT.

38:28.937 --> 38:32.541
I JUST DON'T KNOW
IF IT'S POSSIBLE ANYMORE...

38:34.443 --> 38:36.615
NOT NOW...

38:36.615 --> 38:39.648
NOT WITH US.

38:53.962 --> 38:56.565
